OL,3,CWorld's first carbon tax on
OL,4,Cagriculture to cost farmers #75 per cow
OL,6,FDairy farmers in Denmark will have to
OL,7,Fpay an annual tax of 672 krone (around
OL,8,F#75) per cow due to the planet-heating
OL,9,Femissions they generate.
OL,11,FIt is the world's first carbon
OL,12,Femissions tax on agriculture, and
OL,13,Fwhile it has been broadly welcomed by
OL,14,FDenmark's dairy industry, the move has
OL,15,Fangered some farmers.
OL,17,FThe country's coalition government
OL,18,Fagreed on the tax this week, with new
OL,19,Flevies on livestock due to start in
OL,20,F2030.
