OL,3,CWorld's first carbon tax on
OL,4,Cagriculture to cost farmers #75 per cow
OL,6,FDenmark is a major dairy and pork
OL,7,Fexporter, and agriculture is the
OL,8,Fcountry's biggest source of emissions.
OL,10,FA share of this pollution comes from
OL,11,Fmethane, a potent planet-warming gas
OL,12,Fproduced by cows and some other
OL,13,Fanimals through their burps and manure.
OL,15,FThe tax, expected to be approved by
OL,16,FDenmark's parliament later this year,
OL,17,Fwill amount to 300 krone (around #35)
OL,18,Fper tonne of CO2-equivalent emissions
OL,19,Ffrom livestock from 2030, rising to
OL,20,F750 krone (around #85) in 2035.
