OL,3,CWorld's first carbon tax on
OL,4,Cagriculture to cost farmers #75 per cow
OL,6,FA 60% tax break will apply, meaning
OL,7,Fthat farmers will effectively be
OL,8,Fcharged 120 krone (around #15) per
OL,9,Ftonne of livestock emissions per year
OL,10,Ffrom 2030, rising to 300 krone (around
OL,11,F#35) in 2035.
OL,13,FUsing the lower tax rate results in a
OL,14,Fcharge of around #75 per cow, with the
OL,15,Flevy rising to 1,680 krone (around
OL,16,F#190) per cow in 2035.
