OL,3,CWorld's first carbon tax on
OL,4,Cagriculture to cost farmers #75 per cow
OL,6,FThe agreement also entails investing
OL,7,F40 billion krone (around #4.5 billion)
OL,8,Fin measures including reforestation
OL,9,Fand establishing wetlands in a bid to
OL,10,Fmeet the nation's climate goals.
OL,12,FIn a statement Foreign Minister Lars
OL,13,FLokke Rasmussen said: "With today's
OL,14,Fagreement, we are investing billions
OL,15,Fin the biggest transformation of the
OL,16,FDanish landscape in recent times. At
OL,17,Fthe same time, we will be the first
OL,18,Fcountry in the world with a (carbon)
OL,19,Ftax on agriculture."
