OL,6,FIt comes just months after farmers
OL,7,Fheld protests across Europe ` blocking
OL,8,Froads with tractors and pelting the
OL,9,FEuropean Parliament with eggs over a
OL,10,Flong list of grievances, including
OL,11,Fgripes about environmental regulation
OL,12,Fand excessive red tape.
OL,14,FDanish farmers' group Bredygtigt
OL,15,FLandbrug described the new measures as
OL,16,Fa "scary experiment". Chairman Peter
OL,17,FKir said: "We believe that the
OL,18,Fagreement is pure bureaucracy.
