OL,6,F"We recognise that there is a climate
OL,7,Fproblem... But we do not believe that
OL,8,Fthis agreement will solve the
OL,9,Fproblems, because it will put a spoke
OL,10,Fin the wheel of agriculture's green
OL,11,Finvestments."
OL,13,FPeder Tuborgh, the CEO of Arla Foods,
OL,14,FEurope's largest dairy group, said the
OL,15,Fagreement was "positive" but that
OL,16,Ffarmers who "genuinely do everything
OL,17,Fthey can to reduce emissions" should
OL,18,Fnot be subjected to a tax.
